How to deploy Hadoop automaticlly?

Solution One:
    -deploy.sh: deploy Hadoop on one VM
    -ssh-config.sh: configure ssh
    -sync.sh: sync the sets to each VMs        
    -clear.sh: clear the mess of wrong operation
Solution Two:
    Only store one copy of conf and use NFS to share
